videos.description: D'Angelo Brewer runs it in from the one-yard line for Tulsa's first touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: Tulsa strikes first with rushing TD

videos.description: Tulsa quarterback Chad President keeps the ball and breaks for a 71-yard run which leads to a short Golden Hurricane's touchdown.
videos.headline: President's 71-yard run sets up Tulsa TD

videos.description: Navy's quarterback Zach Abey keeps it and runs into the end zone from the one-yard line to cut Tulsa's lead.
videos.headline: Navy scores on a 1-yard TD run

videos.description: Quarterback Zach Abey scores his second rushing touchdown, this time from the three-yard line, to tie the game.
videos.headline: Navy ties game with short TD

videos.description: Navy's Zach Abey pitches it to Malcom Perry who breaks off a big run for a touchdown to extend the Midshipmen's lead.
videos.headline: Perry rips off 27-yard TD run to extend Navy's lead

videos.description: Navy quarterback Zach Abey keeps the ball and runs into the end zone from the two-yard line to stretch the Midshipmen's lead.
videos.headline: Abey gets third rushing TD of the day

videos.description: Chad President connects with Chris Minter for a 4-yard touchdown pass to cut Navy's lead in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Tulsa closes the gap  with 4-yard TD pass
